## Proposed changes

Add scan_thread_num property for workload group;
```
// means using be config doris_scanner_thread_pool_thread_num
alter workload group normal properties ( 'scan_thread_num'='-1' ); 

// limit workload group's scan thread pool's thread to 16
// it overwrites doris_scanner_thread_pool_thread_num
alter workload group normal properties ( 'scan_thread_num'='16' ); 
```

